  "instructions": [
    "Cut the potato, onion, and red bell pepper into 1-inch cubes.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onion and potato to the skillet and cook until the onion is translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the asparagus and bell pepper to the skillet and cook until the asparagus is tender, about 3 minutes.",
